data.description:
## TYPES

- SILICON FOLEY CATHETERS

- SPECIAL FOLEY CATHETERS
- SELF-RETAINING URINARY CATHETERS
- RED-LATEX URETHRAL CATHETERS
- NELATON CATHETERS
- HYDROPHILIC INTERMMITENT CATHETERS
- MALE EXTERNAL CATHETERS

## FEATURES
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile
- Medical grade materials
- Hydrofylic finish available
- Smooth surface
- Centric positioned cuff
- No presence of foreign particles nor dots
- Fully sealed and undamaged packaging

## COMPONENTS
- Urine Drainage connection
- tubing
- Bladder opening
- cuff
- Cuff inflating vale
